Typo Recent Comments sidebar plugin

* INSTALL

Download Typo Recent Comments and unpack it into vendor/plugins or go to your Typo application and:

./script/plugin install git://github.com/fdv/recent_comments_sidebar.git


Then, go to http://yourdomain/admin/sidebar and enable Typo Recent Comments sidebar plugin.

* REQUIREMENTS

Typo Recent Comments sidebar needs Typo version 4.1 or greater. Typo is at http://typosphere.org or http://github.com/fdv/typo/tree